Title: "Deck.gl for R"
Version: 0.1.0
Description: "R htmlwidget bindings for deck.gl, a WebGL-powered framework for visual exploratory data analysis of large datasets. Create interactive visualizations using deck.gl JSON specifications with server-side data hydration via DuckDB."
